Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[hissing]\NMm hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.40,0:00:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[hiss]\NMm hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.34,0:00:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Antoine believes what\Nhe eats is{\i1} his{\i0} business.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do other predators\Nfeel that way, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.08,0:00:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Would any prey\Nlike to respond?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Muriel? Does it bother you\Nwhen Antoine tries to eat you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because you're\Non opposite ends
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.89,0:00:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,of the food chain doesn't\Nmean you can't work toge--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.23,0:00:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean you can't--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.44,0:00:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.80,0:00:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean you\Ncan't work togeth--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.38,0:00:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I'm sorry, but the\Nmore you distract everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.61,0:00:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the longer this will take.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.68,0:00:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I AM listening to you, but if\Nyou really want to be heard,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:00:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you should join our\NPredator-Prey-Support Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.52,0:00:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you could talk\Nto everyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.29,0:00:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You could teach all\Nthese hungry predators
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.43,0:01:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the delights of a\Ncarrot-based cuisine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I think {\i1}somebunny{\i0} just\Nwants a little attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.64,0:01:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, since we all\Nneed to get along,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,what if all Predators promised\Nto only eat vegetables
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.71,0:01:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,while staying at\Nthe Sanctuary?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sandra.\NYou can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.29,0:01:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.29,0:01:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] Angel! Sandra! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.31,0:01:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. It might look like chaos,\Nbut Fluttershy makes it work,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,even {\i1}with{\i0} Angel running around.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.91,0:01:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Oooh. Perhaps I can help{\i0}\N{\i1} those two get along,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.62,0:01:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} before something here{\i0}\N{\i1} can go terribly wrong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.06,0:02:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Zecora found this little guy\Nand brought him to my office,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but I thought he might do\Nbetter at the sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.91,0:02:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bringing him here seemed{\i0}\N{\i1}the right thing to do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.91,0:02:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've never seen geckos breathe{\i0}\N{\i1}smoke, though, have you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:03:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I certainly haven't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we could take\Na look at his diet,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,plus it's about\Ntime for me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.29,0:03:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to give all the animals\Nhere a check up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a wonderful idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If we really want to\Nknow what's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,we need to make sure the\Nproblem isn't your food.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably just\Nsomething he's been eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um! Is there anything\Nelse we can do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Ahh! Seeing what{\i0}\N{\i1} you two do,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} the real question{\i0}\N{\i1} is: "Can I help YOU?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean... me and Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.79,0:03:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mm hm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's fine!\NWe're fine... I-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't always have\Ntime to indulge him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're best friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:03:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even the best of friends{\i0}\N{\i1}need help from time to time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come visit me in my hut,{\i0}\N{\i1}should you change your mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, thanks! But Angel\Nand I are great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Goodness,\NFluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the list of\Nwhat you do every day!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you find time\Nfor anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Between here and teaching at\Nthe school, I'm not sure I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to love\Nit here, little gecko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? Not\Nfluffy enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to see if your\Nfood is causing your issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.25,0:04:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm. Not now, Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.19,0:04:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They're snake treats\Nmade to look like
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,chocolate chip cookies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They're vegan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:04:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie made a\Nwhole jar of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all yours\Nif you promise....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No more trying to eat\NMuriel the Baby Elephant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.11,0:05:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Angel. I have\Ntoo much to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.16,0:05:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Careful, girl. That neck\Nis still pretty sore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to shift\Nyour weight, Scout.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What does she want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Her neck is feeling better,\Nbut a massage every day
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,for the next week wouldn't\Nhurt. I'll add it to my list.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. Fluttershy, I've said it\Nbefore, but I'll say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This place would be\Na {\i1}zoo{\i0} without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"Listen to you for once?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just WHAT exactly is\Nthat supposed to mean!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.93,0:06:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back! I meant\Ntell me, not... oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you're the only one\Nhe can tell about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Li'l fella just wants\Nyou all to himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately,\Nthat's not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, he's not causing\Nany real trouble..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[crash]\NAh!\N[birds squawk]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Other than that, possibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[crash]\N[elephant trumpets]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Or that. I'll just\Nstop talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[groan] I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope this is\Nimportant, Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've barely made a dent in\Nmy to-do list for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Concentrated\NCarrot Extract?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for reviving\Nenergy-sapped herbivores.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling run down?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You just like the\Ntaste!? Ah! Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:06:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That extract is\Nin short supply!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:07:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you?\NEvery day this week
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you've been causing trouble\Nwhen I have work to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course{\i0} I know you\Ncan't talk to anypony else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.03,0:07:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not MY fault.\NI have responsibilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. We\Ncan't go on like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we do need to\Nsee Zecora for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} No need to sit{\i0}\N{\i1} and silently stew.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.18,0:07:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Tell each other{\i0}\N{\i1} what's bothering you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so impatient, even when\Nhe knows I have work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's not true!\NWe talk all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course talking at\Nthe Sanctuary counts;
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that's where I am when I\Ndon't have a class to teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean,\Nthat's the problem!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You feel like I'm the\Nonly pony you can talk to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and all I do is ignore you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, {\i1}I{\i0} feel like\Nyou don't care
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,about my responsibilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.55,0:08:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh.. Um, as you can see, we're\Nkind of at an impasse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.72,0:08:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Ahh, such luck your{\i0}\N{\i1} coming here, indeed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Behold, the antidote{\i0}\N{\i1} you need.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.12,0:08:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is... this what you\Nmeant by "help us"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.73,0:08:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} When trouble brews{\i0}\N{\i1} between you two,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} turning sister{\i0}\N{\i1} against brother.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} True understanding{\i0}\N{\i1} is what's due,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} each must come to{\i0}\N{\i1} know the other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} There's no time to{\i0}\N{\i1} waste, go directly home,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} but you both must taste{\i0}\N{\i1} when you're finally alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet, Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Zecora told us to take it\Ntogether when we got home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I suppose we could dust\Noff the ol' picnic blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be just\Nlike old times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll drink the\Npotion and settle in
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,for a nice tea party.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can barely remember\Nthe last time we did that!|
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been so busy\Nat the Sanctuary...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Though.. I really need to keep\Nan eye on Zecora's gecko
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and I haven't finished\Nany of today's chores...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't, the animals won't\Nget the care they need!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Maybe we should save\Nthe potion until aft--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel! Zecora said\Nto go home first!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.13,0:09:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}know{\i0} she said we have\Nto take it together so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I have to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what it's\Ngoing to dooWHOOOAA.-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa whoa whoa! Hang on, hold\Nup, am I a pony!? Why am I a pony!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeeeek!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.36,0:09:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ [dramatic sting] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Question: did we\Nswitch bodies?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.72,0:09:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:10:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, I'm a\Npony? La la la la!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Talking is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think this was what\NZecora meant to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you gonna do\Nyour {\i1}chores{\i0}!? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's{\i0} what you're\Nworried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Pff. Well, maybe I don't\NWANNA switch back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only been able to\Ntalk to YOU since we met,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.89,0:10:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and now I can talk\Nto anypony I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Roses are red,\Nviolets are blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,you sell flowers\Nand so do you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Rubber baby buggy bumpers!\NRubber baby buggy bumpers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Toy boat! Toy boat!\NToy boa-AH!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so too listening! Quit\Nbein' so bossy because -- Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there carrots around here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You think Zecora gave\Nus the wrong potion,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,so you're gonna go to\Nher hut in the forest
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and get something\Nto switch us back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You REALLY don't know what\Nit's like being a bunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:11:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck with {\i1}that{\i0}. I'm\Ngonna go find those carrots.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"I need to finish your\Nchores?" Ha, ha, ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't work for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And caring about other\Nanimals is a {\i1}you{\i0} thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [horror sting] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}stare{\i0}!? You\Ncan still do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! No fair making me do your\Nbidding against my will!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.81,0:11:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [horror film music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I'll go\Ndo your lame chores
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,while you go see Zecora.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Anypony know where\Nthat useless list
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,of Fluttershy's chores is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.27,0:11:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Fauna: Hey, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I was starting to wonder\Nif you'd make it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy! Oh,\Nyeah! Uh, that's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely Fluttershy,\Na hundred percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,See how.. {\i1}shy{\i0} I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:11:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I talk to animals...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.25,0:12:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to\Nmarry Discord...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Your list is\Nover there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Yeah. There's my\Ngood ol' list of chores
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that I will absolutely\NNOT rush through
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,because I definitely do not\Nhave better things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.24,0:12:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember {\i1}me{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh. I hope the gem tart stall\Nis still there again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.41,0:12:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I could use a snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You nearly bought every tart\Nthey had last time, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine they\Nwouldn't show up
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.42,0:12:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,when there's a great\Ncustomer like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.59,0:12:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Hi, Angel.\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what\Nhe's trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Angel. You should\Nprobably find Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If I see her, I'll let her\Nknow you're looking for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,AND we're gonna keep\Nat it until you start
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to develop a\Ntaste for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, check Muriel's trunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.97,0:13:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, seems fine to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we don't\Nneed those keys..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway. Let's see. Massage\NClementine's neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Get Scout to switch legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh. Probably best not to wake him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the thing with the\Nthing, yada, yada, yada,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.89,0:13:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,animals, animals, animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left is.. monitor\NZecora's gecko until bedtime!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.60,0:13:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, dude. How\Nabout we do bedtime now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, eating makes\Nme tired too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Which reminds me, there's\Nsome carrot extract
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.14,0:14:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,with my name on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,OK! Let's get you fed\Nand off to dreamland.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.41,0:14:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you eat, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaddya say, Snake? Can you\Nfind something else to eat
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,if I borrow those cookies\Nfor my friend here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure\Nthat's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.\NProblem solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see what's so\Nhard about this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy is\NSUCH a whiner!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Quite a day, my fuzzy friend!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Did things work out{\i0}\N{\i1} for you in the end?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} I'm sorry, dear bunny,{\i0}\N{\i1} that things seem so grave,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} but I don't understand{\i0}\N{\i1} when you sign and wave.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A single link to all the world.{\i0}\N{\i1} only one in all the land.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} How special she must be to{\i0}\N{\i1} you, the one who understands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Perhaps if you explained{\i0}\N{\i1} what you wanted{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} to somepony who understood,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} if you truly felt{\i0}\N{\i1} heard and valued,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} all would return to good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} And if you were{\i0}\N{\i1} to both apologize,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} having learned{\i0}\N{\i1} this little lesson,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} I imagine that{\i0}\N{\i1} might bring an end{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} to the friendship{\i0}\N{\i1} therapy session.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.77,0:15:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:15:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Fauna: Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.09,0:16:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mind helping me look\Nfor Muriel the Baby Elephant?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's having\Ndinner with Antoine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Antoine the PYTHON!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It was on the list:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.93,0:16:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"Remember Antoine wants to\Nhave Muriel over for dinner."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Not{\i1} over{\i0} for dinner! He\Nwants to have her FOR DINNER!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.11,0:16:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. WHAT!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.30,0:16:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.72,0:16:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad snake! Open your mouth\Nthis instant, Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [tense music] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.97,0:16:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on!? You did\Nall the chores on your list.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!? Didn't you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, technically,\NI did'em, kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.21,0:16:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But more technically,\Nit's not {\i1}my{\i0} list.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You wrote it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:16:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT'S GOTTEN INTO YOU!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You do NOT wanna know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong\Nwith her... him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He's exhausted!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.04,0:17:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, I need a jar
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.34,0:17:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,of concentrated\Ncarrot extract, STAT!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.84,0:17:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's locked in\Nthe supply room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are your keys!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Any ideas how to get the\Nkeys out of the elephant
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.89,0:17:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that's inside the snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,OK! Point taken. And\NI totally deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not provide you with the\Ncare that Fluttershy would.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But NOW you know\Nwhat it's like
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.03,0:17:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,not to get the\Nlevel of attention
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.43,0:17:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to which you've\Nbecome accustomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The point is Fluttershy is\Ntrapped in my bunny body
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and if we don't help\Nher, maybe none of us
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,will get her attention. I get\Nthat you don't want to help {\i1}me{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:17:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but don't you want to help {\i1}her{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ [military snare drum] ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.59,0:18:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.16,0:18:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.24,0:18:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we just need to get\Nthose keys out of there..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.12,0:18:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha! Nice\None, snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.42,0:18:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess Fluttershy was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Predators and prey\N{\i1}can{\i0} work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is so. Much. Work!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:19:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I know. I have no clue\Nhow you do it all,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.34,0:19:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but we are so grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.84,0:19:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.42,0:19:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe she\Ndoes this every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wish I could\Ntell her myself..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.17,0:19:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.37,0:19:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"It was so hard getting\Nto Zecora's hut?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And impossible getting back?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't believe I\Nsurvive like this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't believe\N{\i1}you{\i0} work here every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.31,0:19:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,These animals are crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.35,0:19:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder you don't\Nhave time for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My life is hard? No,\NYOUR life is hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You never appreciated me?\NNo, I never appreciated {\i1}you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.06,0:19:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sorry? I'm sorry too!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:20:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, you little bunny\Nwho's a pony who's a bunny! Ooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my goodness! I'm\Nback! I'm a pony again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Angel, I promise to always\Nmake time for you from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean maybe I won't\Nhave to? You want to do.. WHAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...and that's when I realized
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy doesn't have to\Nbe the only one I talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.00,0:20:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can come here and\Ntalk to all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.87,0:20:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And now that I know how much\Nwork goes into this place,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I could kinda, sorta\Nhelp out every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.51,0:20:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Angel! That is so sweet,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but now that I know what\Nyou go through every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand why your time\Nwith me is so important.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise to always\Nmake time for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Turns out your friend, here,\Ndoesn't have a problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.17,0:21:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He isn't a gecko.\NHe's a fire lizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot that before\Nthey get their flame,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.74,0:21:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,it's hard to\Ntell them apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} I'm glad to discover where{\i0}\N{\i1} the source of it lies,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} or the fire that he breathes{\i0}\N{\i1} would be quite the surprise.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of surprises...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you please\N{\i1}never{\i0} do that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,♪♪
